race.description: Cancer Council Stars Country Boosted Mdn Hcp
race.comment: SUPREME STATEMENT (1) hard fit now and has a host of gear changes for this. Stalked the speed with the 59kg before folding up in the straight when last over 1400m at Randwick Kensington. Earlier runs were good and sure to be thereabouts. RAINBOW BLESSING (3) strengthened up over the break and the blinkers go on third-up. Senior rider booked and a win looks imminent after finishing third over 1400m at Scone. PURPLE PRINCE (8) nine start maiden who drops in trip after failing to make an impression when seventh over 1500m at Muswellbrook. Place chance. FASHION SPREE (5) handy filly who finished seventh last start but was beaten only 1.75 lengths over 1200m at Port Macquarie. Worth including.
